12.1.6 Repeat Count
-------------------

Any command in copy mode can be prefixed with a number (by pressing
digits `0...9') which is taken as a repeat count. Example:
     C-a C-[ H 10 j 5 Y
   will copy lines 11 to 15 into the paste buffer.


